review_blob: Pure class! Best Norwegian Christmas beer 2013. Nice color, complex taste with sweet taste of Christmas.
Cool bottle, nice santa! Nice appearance, pours dark. Dominant coffee taste. A little to much alcohol taste. Complex finish. Taste better with some Bjorn Hellfuck on the stereo.
Pours pale color, smells like standard IPA, watery taste with some bitterness, way to bitter finish. Shite.
